## Required Transition Conditions

### Transition: `draft` → `brief_ready`
Trigger:
- required Brief fields have been completed

Minimum condition:
- Project Context is sufficiently filled
- Hackathon Context is sufficiently filled

UI result:
- Room / Pitch becomes available
- primary CTA changes to record pitch

### Transition: `brief_ready` → `pitch_recorded`
Trigger:
- user completes the pitch recording flow successfully

Minimum condition:
- pitch artifact is saved
- recording metadata exists

UI result:
- Room / Q&A becomes unlocked
- primary CTA changes to start Q&A

### Transition: `pitch_recorded` → `qa_completed`
Trigger:
- Q&A session ends successfully

Minimum condition:
- enough turn data / transcript data exists
- session is finalized

UI result:
- Debrief / Review becomes available for generation
- primary CTA changes to generate review

### Transition: `qa_completed` → `debrief_ready`
Trigger:
- debrief generation succeeds

Minimum condition:
- review artifact exists

UI result:
- Review becomes accessible
- Coach becomes unlocked
- primary CTA changes to open coach or review findings

### Transition: `debrief_ready` → `completed`
Trigger:
- user has entered the debrief and session is marked finalized

Minimum condition:
- debrief exists
- session is no longer actively in rehearsal

UI result:
- session is stored in history as completed
- user can revisit or duplicate it

